1
00:00:38,600 --> 00:00:40,560
You've been with me for three years,

2
00:00:40,560 --> 00:00:42,040
and now you betray me.

3
00:00:42,720 --> 00:00:44,000
What you've done,

4
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:45,740
I will keep it a secret.

5
00:00:47,240 --> 00:00:49,160
This is the last piece of dignity I can give you.

6
00:00:49,160 --> 00:00:50,490
Lilian, let me tell you.

7
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:52,560
I did sleep with Danpa.

8
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:54,080
And don't forget,

9
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:56,360
if Danpa and Daihaibo weren't brothers,

10
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:57,820
would he have taken you in?

11
00:00:57,840 --> 00:00:58,840
And I know

12
00:01:00,440 --> 00:01:02,360
you still keep Daihaibo's belongings.

13
00:01:02,360 --> 00:01:03,760
Don't think I don't know.

14
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:05,720
You are the shameless one.

15
00:01:05,720 --> 00:01:06,720
Give it back to me.

16
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,620
Still trying to snatch it?

17
00:01:09,720 --> 00:01:10,250
Dailing.

18
00:01:11,440 --> 00:01:12,080
Ruannila.

19
00:01:13,039 --> 00:01:14,900
You parasite mother and daughter

20
00:01:15,080 --> 00:01:16,940
should get out of the Chen family.

21
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,600
Miss.

22
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,240
Don't cry.

23
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:29,440
I'm sorry.

24
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,340
From now on in the Chen family,

25
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,360
I will be the one

26
00:01:33,560 --> 00:01:34,620
to take care of you.

27
00:01:53,479 --> 00:01:54,340
Foster father.

28
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:55,729
Long time no see.

29
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:06,280
Since you were young,

30
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,580
I have trained you.

31
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,080
For so many years,

32
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:10,639
the tasks I gave you,

33
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,330
you have done very well.

34
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,560
You haven't let me down.

35
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,440
Thank you, foster father.

36
00:02:17,440 --> 00:02:18,640
It's what I should do.

37
00:02:23,640 --> 00:02:25,640
Now that your wings are fully grown,

38
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:28,170
you dare to play tricks behind my back.

39
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:30,000
I've raised you for so many years.

40
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:32,960
Is this how you repay me?

41
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:41,520
I'll give you one last chance.

42
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,720
Make Dailing disappear.

43
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,480
What?

44
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,579
Is there a problem?

45
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:54,840
No.

46
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:57,560
Since you are a blade,

47
00:02:58,280 --> 00:03:00,520
you must draw blood once unsheathed.

48
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:02,400
That is your duty.

49
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,440
If you can't do it,

50
00:03:05,040 --> 00:03:07,760
then there is no need for you to exist.

51
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,690
Understand?

52
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:12,010
Understood.

53
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,460
I will complete your task.

54
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,250
I won't let you down.

55
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:18,560
Go.

56
00:03:35,440 --> 00:03:35,920
Sir,

57
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,490
everything is done.

58
00:03:38,079 --> 00:03:39,880
We adopted ten people this time,

59
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:40,520
among whom

60
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:42,650
this girl is the most talented.

61
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,579
What should we do with her?

62
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,090
Send her abroad.

63
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,760
So,

64
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,880
you still decided to forgive him

65
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,930
and get back together with him.

66
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,930
Since what happened five years ago

67
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:13,780
was just a misunderstanding,

68
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:18,050
I really can't find a reason to reject him.

69
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:26,300
No matter what decision you make,

70
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,250
as long as you are happy,

71
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:33,980
that's the most important thing.

72
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:39,000
I know you've also done a lot for me.

73
00:04:40,280 --> 00:04:40,880
Thank you.

74
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,200
But,

75
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,080
if one day

76
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,940
you get tired of him

77
00:04:53,880 --> 00:04:54,920
or he bullies you,

78
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,010
please remember

79
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,440
that I'm always here.

80
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:01,770
Don't reject me.

81
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:10,000
You didn't reject me,

82
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,820
so I'll take it as a yes.

83
00:05:16,600 --> 00:05:17,660
It's getting late.

84
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,730
Angwei is waiting for me to eat.

85
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,160
Stingy,

86
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,560
unpresentable.

87
00:05:32,159 --> 00:05:34,020
Don't do anything for me anymore.

88
00:05:35,080 --> 00:05:36,080
It's not worth it.

89
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,240
Unpresentable.

90
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:55,720
Little bitch.

91
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:58,460
You finally get what you deserve.

92
00:07:04,600 --> 00:07:05,530
Don't be afraid.

93
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,610
The taste of this injection

94
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:11,010
is far more thrilling than that glass of wine.

95
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,920
You maniac.

96
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:20,940
Do you really think

97
00:07:21,840 --> 00:07:22,960
you can kill me?

98
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,080
Bitch.

99
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,280
Still talking tough.

100
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:35,480
Your life is

101
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:36,920
in my hands now.

102
00:07:37,200 --> 00:07:38,600
Once this needle goes in,

103
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,840
you're dead.

104
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:49,040
Ruan Nila.

105
00:07:50,440 --> 00:07:51,000
Stop.

106
00:07:53,960 --> 00:07:54,440
Stop right there.
